keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmapAll

map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map J scrollPageDown
map K scrollPageUp
map q removeTab
map Q restoreTab
map + Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map = Vomnibar.activate
map gt nextTab
map gT previousTab
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map C duplicateTab
map / enterFindMode
map b performFind
map B performBackwardsFind
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map < goBack
map > goForward
map r reload
